title: Doctors Find Cure For Cancer, Later Found Dead... | Qui West | 99.1 KGGI
text:
Doctors Find Cure For Cancer, Later Found Dead... posted by Qui West - share 
"A Florida doctor Dr. Jeff Bradstreet, M.D., focused heavily on researching the possibility of treating cancer with GcMAF. Yet, a year ago, he was found dead in a river, and his death was immediately reported to be a suicide, even though he had a gunshot to the chest. 
The “suicide” was later found to be a murder and is only one of the 7 mysterious deaths that happened in the same time period. All of the were holistic doctors who investigated the potential of GcMAF to treat and cure this deadly disease." 
SOURCE Qui West began his radio journey in 2006 as an intern in San Francisco where he developed a love for radio. From there, he became a public affairs host and landed a weekend on air spot with KYLD Wild 949. The he hit the majors and worked at Houston's legendary hip hop station KBXX 979 The Box. Qui West hosted the No.1 rated night show in the market for almost 4 years. Most recently, he was home in San Francisco at KRBQ 102. Now he has a new home, right here in the I.E. on 99.1 KGGI. Join him every afternoon from 2-6p and follow him everywhere @QuiWest. Contact
